    "description": "——时为科学世纪。<br>用53分钟就能从首都京都到达东京的全地下新干线『广重』也已经通车。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/e803b26de694b50c830829dbbc93f531.avif?t=1738589935\" width=580 height=200 /></span><br>玛艾露贝莉・赫恩。宇佐见莲子。<br><br>两人现在——<br><br>还尚未相遇。<br><br><br>～游戏概要～<br><br>这是一款以解谜为主的二次创作文字冒险游戏。<br>以上海爱丽丝幻乐团的“秘封俱乐部”系列作为题材。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/e8dac0bdba88329b7459d9d7514e4924.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br>故事发生在秘封俱乐部的第一部作品《莲台野夜行～Ghostly Field Club》之前。<br>游戏开始于大学的入学仪式之后，梅莉和莲子相遇的那一刻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/98220ec20c0a0a9fab904a7e38c91eae.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br>使用从两人对话中获得的记忆“碎片”中导出的词汇<br>最终完成《莲台野夜行》的故事，是这个游戏的目标。<br><br><br>～记忆“碎片”～<br><br>“碎片”系统灵感来源自“合资会社自行车创业”的“ANOS系统”<br>比起以前的文字冒险游戏，该系统带来了全新的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/17252f2e35581bd462249beae4de3f79.poster.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/17252f2e35581bd462249beae4de3f79.webm?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/17252f2e35581bd462249beae4de3f79.mp4?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从故事中获得的文章“碎片”中自由选择词语<br>生成推动故事前进的“关键词”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/c5e3bf42486d0a34ef7ecb3459f1a268.poster.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/c5e3bf42486d0a34ef7ecb3459f1a268.webm?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/c5e3bf42486d0a34ef7ecb3459f1a268.mp4?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果在剧情节点设定相应关键词，就会走上分支路线。<br>可以看到新的剧情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/57d94802e3bbe7b1c5a0bb44a9c0f6e9.poster.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/57d94802e3bbe7b1c5a0bb44a9c0f6e9.webm?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/57d94802e3bbe7b1c5a0bb44a9c0f6e9.mp4?t=1738589935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>因为并不能像以前的冒险游戏那样，单纯尝试每一个选项，<br>所以，只是漫不经心地阅读文章是无法通关本作的。<br><br><br><br>命运有“不同路径”，人生却没有“选项”——<br><br>秘封俱乐部的两人，能打开莲台野的入口吗……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643060/extras/fee9e983edd7f00d9d9a1ffcb9209222.avif?t=1738589935\" width=500 height=374 /></span>",
